scripts.fetch: npm run fetch-package-json && npm run fetch-deep-json
scripts.fetch-package-json: npm install @deep-foundation/payments-tinkoff-c2b-test@latest --no-save && (if [ -f ./node_modules/@deep-foundation/payments-tinkoff-c2b-test/package.json ]; then rm -f ./package.json; fi;) && mv node_modules/@deep-foundation/payments-tinkoff-c2b-test/package.json ./
scripts.fetch-deep-json: npm install @deep-foundation/payments-tinkoff-c2b-test@latest --no-save && (if [ -f ./node_modules/@deep-foundation/payments-tinkoff-c2b-test/deep.json ]; then rm -f ./deep.json; fi;) && mv node_modules/@deep-foundation/payments-tinkoff-c2b-test/deep.json ./
